   Latest Release
   This series of reports simplifies the science of research findings for
   the educated lay public, legislators, educational groups, and
   practitioners. The series reports on research findings of national
   interest.
     * Anabolic Steroid Abuse [Revised 2000]
     * Cocaine: Abuse and Addiction [Printed 1999]
          + Also Available in Spanish [Printed 2001]
     * New! Hallucinogens and Dissociative Drugs [Printed 2001]
     * Heroin: Abuse and Addiction [Printed 1997]
     * Inhalant Abuse [Revised 2000]
          + Also Available in Spanish [Printed 2001]
     * Methamphetamine: Abuse and Addiction [Printed 1998]
          + Also Available in Spanish [Printed 2000]
     * Nicotine Addiction [Printed 1998]
     * New! Prescription Drugs Abuse and Addiction [Printed 2001]
          + Also Available in Spanish [Printed 2001]
